And, coming from one of the most trusted names in America, you know that this entire selection of appliances is as advanced as it is practical. Color: Black.

205974857.Title: GE 36 in. Radiant Electric Cooktop in Black with 5 Elements Including Power Boil
205974857.Description: Your GE 36 in. Electric Cooktop in Black has 5 radiant cooking elements that cook foods quickly and evenly on this sleek, glass surface. The ribbon heating elements ensure even heat and fast warm-up times. You can use different pan sizes on the single 8 in. x 5 in. Power Boil 2400-Watt flexible element that produces rapid powerful heat, plus the center 12 in./9 in./6 in. Tri-Ring burner has up to 3000-Watt of power. Front Center Controls allow for ease of use. GE products offer the best in contemporary design matched with the latest in appliance technologies to transform the way you live. Sporting a bold, dramatic look and state of the art features, this collection provides the perfect combination of style and innovation throughout your kitchen.

205974880.Description: Your GE Profile 36 in. Electric Cooktop in Black has 5 radiant cooking elements that cook foods quickly and evenly on this sleek, glass surface. 301458485.Title: KitchenAid 36 in. Radiant Electric Downdraft Cooktop in Stainless Steel with 5 Elements, Silver
301458485.Description: This 36 in. electric cooktop features Downdraft, an integrated ventilation system that doesn't require a separate hood. A 10 in. EVEN-HEAT ultra-element provides versatility for both high and low-temperature cooking and has multiple simmer settings. And with a 3-speed fan with 300 CFM exhaust rating, the venting can keep up with your culinary feats. Color: Stainless Steel.

300931219.Title: LG STUDIO 36 in. Radiant Electric Cooktop in Stainless Steel with 5 Elements and SmoothTouch Controls, Silver
300931219.Description: Cooking performance meets modern design in this LG radiant cooktop. Steady Heat cooking elements deliver constant heat at any temperature for more precise heat control, and provide a quick response to every temperature adjustment. SmoothTouch controls allow you to adjust the settings with the touch of a finger. Color: Stainless Steel.

306531991.Title: Cafe 36 in. Radiant Electric Cooktop in Black and Brushed Bronze with 5 Elements with Sync-Burners Including Sync-Burners, Black with Brushed Bronze Hardware
306531991.Description: One look at the Cafe kitchen and you'll feel as if you've been transported behind the scenes of your favorite casual dining experience. Each appliance has been meticulously designed to create an atmosphere where people like to gather and love to cook. Tough stainless steel and powerful elements complement their robust appearance. Color: Black with Brushed Bronze Hardware.

307594209.Title: FRIGIDAIRE GALLERY 30 in. Radiant Electric Cooktop in Black with 5 Elements
307594209.Description: Expand your cooking possibilities with this sleek Electric Cooktop by Frigidaire Gallery. The five-element smooth surface cooktop features two Space Wise elements that adjust in size to fit the diameter of your cookware. A 7 in. burner and two 6 in. burners provide even more space to state and sear your favorite foods, giving you flexibility when preparing a picture-perfect meal for family or guests. Express-Select control knobs easily go from warm to boil, so you can regulate your heat output with accuracy. Hot surface indicators let you know when the cooking elements are still too hot to touch, keeping you and your family safe. Color: Black.

308849739.Title: Frigidaire 36 in. Radiant Electric Cooktop in Black with 5 Elements including Quick Boil Element
308849739.Description: Beautiful Ceramic glass cooktop is easy to clean. Features a powerful 3,000-Watt Quick Boil Element, SpaceWise Expandable Element that expands to accommodate various sizes of cookware, a keep warm zone and easy to use ready select controls. With the Frigidaire Fit Promise, we promise that the 36 in. cooktop will fit your existing countertop cutout of the same width and configuration. Color: Black.

202665321.Title: LG Electronics 30 in. Radiant Smooth Surface Electric Cooktop in Black with 5 Elements and SmoothTouch Controls, Smooth Black
202665321.Description: LG's premium 30 in. radiant cooktop is equipped with steady-heat technology to deliver constant heat at any temperature for more precise cooking control. The best part is, the temperature settings respond quickly to power setting adjustments so there is less chance you'll burn your food. LG cooktops truly are style and convenience in perfect harmony. Color: Smooth Black.

311525994.Title: Samsung 36 in. Radiant Electric Cooktop in Black with 5-Elements
311525994.Description: The Samsung Electric Cooktop is stunningly bold with a timeless design for the perfect blend of form and function. It offers a full range of elements for all of your cooking needs. Theres a cooking element for all of your needs, whether you're boiling water, melting chocolate or simmering sauce. Smooth glass ceramic surface and dishwasher safe knobs make cleaning easy. Color: Black.

304812193.Title: Bosch 800 Series 36 in. Radiant Electric Cooktop in Black with 5 Elements including 3,600-Watt SpeedBoost Element
304812193.Description: Bosch cooktops are designed to deliver perfect results with minimal effort. Whether you chose induction, gas, or electric, every Bosch cooktop combines simplicity with intuitive usability. So recipes are followed more efficiently, meals are made quickly, and cleanup happens easily. Because at the end of a long day, Bosch believes cooking should bring joy, not frustration. The 800 Series electric cooktop is sleek in design, and features SpeedBoost which adds even more power to speed up the cooking process. Color: Black.

305455472.Title: Whirlpool 36 in. Radiant Electric Ceramic Glass Cooktop in Black with 5 Elements including a Dual Radiant Element
305455472.Description: Cook all your family's favorites and clean up quick with a 5-burner cooktop designed to make the most of your mealtime routine. The FLEXHEAT dual radiant element gives you flexibility, while the Warm Zone element keeps food warm while you finish cooking. When dinner's done, a ceramic glass cooktop makes it easy to wipe away messes. Color: Black.
